        "_key": "efb8a092487f3"
      },
      {
        "_type": "span",
        "marks": [],
        "text": ", these two videos were created for the launch (below) and re-design (above) of N26's premium product.",
        "_key": "efb8a092487f4"
      }
    ],
    "markDefs": [
      {
